videos.description: Landon Taliaferro and Wynston Tabbs each knock down 3-pointers for Fairfield and Boston College respectively.
videos.headline: Fairfield and Boston College trade 3s early

videos.description: Wynston Tabbs nails his third 3 of the game to give Boston College a 64-52 lead.
videos.headline: Tabbs extends BC lead with 3-pointer
